1995: Art. 102.017. COURT COSTS; COURTHOUSE SECURITY FUND [A> ; MUNICIPAL COURT BUILDING SECURITY FUND <A] . (a) A defendant convicted in a trial for a felony offense in a district court shall pay a $ 5 security fee as a cost of court.

