[A> (2) THE PERSON RECEIVES COMMUNITY SUPERVISION, INCLUDING DEFERRED ADJUDICATION; OR <A]

[A> (3) THE COURT DEFERS FINAL DISPOSITION OF THE PERSON'S CASE. <A]

